@page "/about"

<section class="py-5 bg-light">
    <div class="container">
        <h1 class="fw-bold text-center mb-4">About TravelTayo</h1>
        <p class="lead text-center">
            TravelTayo is your trusted family travel companion, helping you plan memorable adventures
            across Asia and beyond. Our mission is to make travel simple, affordable, and enjoyable
            for parents and kids alike.
        </p>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="py-5 bg-white">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row align-items-center">
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <img src="/images/home-bg-2.jpg"
                     alt="TravelTayo Family Adventures"
                     class="img-fluid rounded shadow" loading="lazy">
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <h2 class="fw-bold">Why We Built TravelTayo</h2>
                <p>
                    We know how stressful it can be to plan a family vacation—searching dozens of sites,
                    comparing hotels, and finding activities that both parents and kids will enjoy.
                    That’s why we created TravelTayo: a single platform designed for families to
                    explore destinations, compare accommodations, and discover exciting activities together.
                </p>
                <p>
                    Whether you're dreaming of island hopping in the Philippines, visiting Disneyland Tokyo,
                    or relaxing in a Bali resort, TravelTayo helps you find the best options in just a few clicks.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="py-5 bg-light">
    <div class="container text-center">
        <h2 class="fw-bold">Powered by Agoda</h2>
        <p>
            TravelTayo partners with Agoda through their affiliate program,
            giving our users access to thousands of verified hotels, resorts, and vacation homes worldwide.
            This means you get trusted listings, secure bookings, and competitive prices—all backed by Agoda’s global network.
        </p>
        <a href="https://www.agoda.com/?cid=1922891"
           target="_blank"
           class="btn btn-primary btn-lg mt-3">Book with Agoda</a>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="py-5 bg-white">
    <div class="container text-center">
        <h2 class="fw-bold">Our Vision</h2>
        <p>
            To be the go-to travel platform for Filipino families and Asian travelers,
            helping create joyful and stress-free adventures for every trip.
        </p>
    </div>
</section>
